{
  "stem": "20978.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As for that matter, not only Pesach, but every-- every Friday night, or Shabbos after a meal, we sat at the table, the table everybody together, and we sang [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, of course, I was asked to [NON-ENGLISH], because I was the younger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was something to look forward to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], for one, for Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the summertime, we used to have cold food, fruit soup, watermelons, summer fruits and things like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, the beautiful challahs she baked, cakes, kindl which was-- still my favorite.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That if I see it, I can't turn away from it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the maid used to go to [NON-ENGLISH] to check the-- the-- what do they call the [NON-ENGLISH], you know, for the-- for the ducks, to see if it's kosher, you know, if it's good.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These are things-- I mean there's many things that-- that comes to me throughout the years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I have my own Seder here with my children and grandchildren it brings back memories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, basically the shul that I belong to is about the same.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It's sukkah, where I always build the sukkah for my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was an exciting thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By numbers, I wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Gentiles was a larger percentage, more-- more goyim than Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 70 and 30.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had some good ones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had non-Jewish friends that lived on the same street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they offered to hide me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Don't forget, it's over 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't remember their names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I would not leave my mother and my sister and brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Without me they would have never survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
